## Installation

Latest release:

Recommended, with conda:
```sh 
conda install -c conda-forge cartes
```

or with pip:
```sh
pip install cartes
```

Development version:

```sh
git clone https://github.com/xoolive/cartes
cd cartes
pip install .
```

